steps.name: Then I should see Database screen display
When I delete all tables in Database menu
When I delete the table with Name "jit012"
Then I should not see the table with Name "jit012" display
When I add new table with Name "jit012a" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit012a" display
When I add new table with Name "jit012b" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit012b" display
When I drag the table Name "jit012b" to new location with x: "200", y: "0"
When I trigger relation popup established from table Name "jit012a" to table Name "jit012b"
When I check radio button popup Name "has many"
When I update popup with dropdown Name "Target" to value "jit012bs"
Then I should see textbox popup Name "Foreign key" has value "jit012a_id"
When I check checkbox popup Name "nullable"
When I press Save button modal popup
Then I should see the realtion path display
Then I should see column with name "jit012bs" and index "4" of table name "jit012a" has type "Model" display
Then I should see column with name "jit012a_id" and index "4" of table name "jit012b" has type "foreign_key" display
When I open relation popup of pair "jit012a-jit012b"
Then I should see radio button popup Name "has many" is checked
Then I should see dropdown popup Name "Target" has value "jit012bs"
Then I should see checkbox popup Name "nullable" is checked
When I close the modal popup
When I delete relation path of pair "jit012a-jit012b"
Then I should not see the realtion path display
When I delete all tables in Database menu
